  (x , 𝟘∞) ·× (𝟘∞ , y) ≡⟨ refl ⟩
  (x ·∞ 𝟘∞ , 𝟘∞ ·∞ y)  ≡⟨ cong₂ _,_ (0∞-absorbs-right x) (0∞-absorbs-left y) ⟩
